[FRENCH]

00:00:31.480 --> 00:00:34.480
I was just Shri Mataji, explaining a bit the chakras.

00:00:34.680 --> 00:00:38.720
So I explained, I explained the different two sides

00:00:38.920 --> 00:00:41.720
SM:- Two sides
SY:- The right and left side,

00:00:41.920 --> 00:00:44.280
the centers of energy

00:00:44.480 --> 00:00:50.280
and that's all I've told.
SM - All right. Thank you.

00:00:50.480 --> 00:00:53.280
SY - But we made a beautiful introduction before.

00:00:53.480 --> 00:00:56.720
SM - All right.

00:01:36.200 --> 00:01:41.680
I bow to all the seekers of truth.

00:01:47.640 --> 00:01:53.600
The truth can be realized

00:01:53.800 --> 00:01:57.480
if you love someone.

00:01:59.360 --> 00:02:03.480
But it should be pure love,

00:02:05.080 --> 00:02:09.720
without any lust and greed

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:16.880
which is a Divine love.

00:02:17.760 --> 00:02:21.920
Divine love doesn't expect anything.

00:02:24.640 --> 00:02:27.480
You cannot sell it,

00:02:28.480 --> 00:02:35.280
you cannot force it on anyone.

00:02:38.720 --> 00:02:43.400
It is the purity

00:02:43.600 --> 00:02:48.480
of your being, that starts emitting that love.

00:02:54.520 --> 00:02:59.800
For example there's a lamp, which is dirty,

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.800
and even if you put a light inside that

00:03:05.000 --> 00:03:08.480
it won't give any light at all.

00:03:17.080 --> 00:03:20.520
So the first process that starts in you

00:03:20.720 --> 00:03:25.360
of the awakening of the Kundalini

00:03:29.960 --> 00:03:35.720
gives you the feeling of the All-pervading power

00:03:39.360 --> 00:03:44.760
and also gives you a kind of a peace within and a security.

00:03:48.640 --> 00:03:51.680
But above all you develop

00:03:51.880 --> 00:03:57.480
a new awareness called as collective consciousness.

00:04:01.480 --> 00:04:04.080
This new consciousness is where

00:04:04.280 --> 00:04:08.680
you can feel another person on your finger tips

00:04:13.880 --> 00:04:17.760
and you start emitting yourself

00:04:17.960 --> 00:04:21.480
in vibrations of Divine Love.

00:04:25.640 --> 00:04:32.440
But these vibrations are very dim in the beginning.

00:04:36.560 --> 00:04:40.480
The Kundalini comes, again falls down,

00:04:40.680 --> 00:04:44.920
again attends to the problems in the being.

00:04:54.560 --> 00:04:58.720
The problems could be physical,

00:05:01.480 --> 00:05:05.400
could be mental, could be emotional.

00:05:06.600 --> 00:05:13.720
But the main problem is the spiritual problem

00:05:16.520 --> 00:05:19.560
which is very difficult to eradicate.

00:05:22.240 --> 00:05:29.480
But as you start seeing your own problems and blockades

00:05:32.120 --> 00:05:37.800
and feeling on, feeling them on your fingertips,

00:05:40.000 --> 00:05:45.600
you yourself correct your own being

00:05:47.600 --> 00:05:52.760
as if you have become your own guide and your own master.

00:05:55.120 --> 00:06:00.400
In your own light you start seeing what's wrong with you.

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:07.560
I don't have to tell you that this is wrong, that is wrong.

00:06:07.760 --> 00:06:11.480
You yourself correct yourself.

00:06:15.720 --> 00:06:21.840
When this process starts of cleansing the purity improves within.

00:06:31.160 --> 00:06:38.360
That is your attention becomes very pure.

00:06:42.800 --> 00:06:46.280
When you look at something as I told you yesterday

00:06:46.480 --> 00:06:50.320
there's no thought that comes into your mind,

00:06:55.920 --> 00:06:58.800
but you become a witness.

00:07:00.080 --> 00:07:03.680
But it's not only that.

00:07:03.880 --> 00:07:06.120
In collective consciousness

00:07:06.320 --> 00:07:11.600
when you look at something, you pay attention to something,

00:07:11.800 --> 00:07:14.600
it gets purified.

00:07:23.800 --> 00:07:29.480
That's why Christ has said "Thou shalt not have adulterous eyes."

00:07:32.920 --> 00:07:38.360
That means in your eyes there should not be any lust or greed.

00:07:42.840 --> 00:07:46.800
When you look at people

00:07:47.040 --> 00:07:51.160
then there should not be any lust

00:07:51.360 --> 00:07:55.240
or feeling of greed but just you look at them

00:07:55.440 --> 00:08:00.320
and the purity of your eyes is purifying them.

00:08:11.480 --> 00:08:18.480
You all are capable of becoming that kind of a strong personality,

00:08:22.040 --> 00:08:27.360
the light of Spirit, now enlightened within you.

00:08:30.720 --> 00:08:34.840
Spirit first of all gives you the truth,

00:08:37.320 --> 00:08:39.920
the absolute,

00:08:40.120 --> 00:08:43.760
because the Spirit is absolute.

00:08:45.320 --> 00:08:48.640
It gives you the absolute truth into such an extent

00:08:48.840 --> 00:08:54.640
that even if you have ten children and tie up their eyes

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:06.800
and ask them "What's wrong with this person?"

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:13.360
they will all raise this finger,

00:09:15.880 --> 00:09:19.000
means this finger is burning.

00:09:20.600 --> 00:09:27.920
That means that that person is suffering from guilt.

00:09:34.480 --> 00:09:38.480
That means this is the center which is catching, here.

00:09:40.600 --> 00:09:43.880
So much is the absoluteness of the truth is.

00:09:47.200 --> 00:09:51.960
That means our brain captures the absolute truth.

00:09:58.160 --> 00:10:05.480
Now, our attention becomes collectively conscious as I told you.

00:10:07.800 --> 00:10:10.440
Like we see the television,

00:10:10.640 --> 00:10:13.640
the play is going on somewhere in the central place,

00:10:13.840 --> 00:10:16.480
and we see the television.

00:10:23.600 --> 00:10:30.480
So, say I am sitting here and My attention has gone somewhere else

00:10:33.280 --> 00:10:39.000
to some person, maybe to some problem to anything.

00:10:42.480 --> 00:10:46.480
But it's not like television, it's more than that,

00:10:48.480 --> 00:10:53.480
because this acts through the subtle of the ether,

00:10:57.360 --> 00:11:03.480
that when this attention goes to the other end, it acts.

00:11:09.560 --> 00:11:17.480
It works, it organizes, it sends information everywhere

00:11:19.360 --> 00:11:23.320
and the whole cosmos works it out.

00:11:24.000 --> 00:11:28.840
And then the action takes place, instantaneously.

00:11:30.040 --> 00:11:33.480
And you are amazed how it works.

00:11:34.360 --> 00:11:37.440
You might say it's a miracle

00:11:37.960 --> 00:11:43.320
but everything that is Divine is miraculous to human beings.

00:11:46.240 --> 00:11:49.480
It acts in so many ways.

00:11:52.080 --> 00:11:55.960
There was - there are so many stories,

00:11:56.480 --> 00:12:01.480
Sahaja Yogis will be able to tell you about the miracles.

00:12:04.560 --> 00:12:09.560
So this attention has got vibrations in it.

00:12:12.680 --> 00:12:18.280
These vibrations are the ones which

00:12:18.480 --> 00:12:22.280
themselves are knowledgeable.

00:12:25.920 --> 00:12:29.160
They have the knowledge

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:32.680
and they know what to do

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:37.280
and they are connected with the whole.

00:12:38.880 --> 00:12:43.880
So the message from them goes into the cosmos

00:12:46.280 --> 00:12:52.120
and it's such a beautiful, efficient

00:12:52.320 --> 00:12:56.160
machine, we can say - it's not a good word though,

00:12:56.360 --> 00:12:59.880
of energy that

00:13:00.080 --> 00:13:06.440
it acts instantaneously in the proper way.

00:13:14.880 --> 00:13:18.640
Some people ask Me, "Mother if these powers come into us,

00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:22.480
we can use it for wrong things."

00:13:27.880 --> 00:13:33.480
You cannot. If you try, your vibrations will stop.

00:13:34.560 --> 00:13:36.560
If somebody falsely says that

00:13:36.760 --> 00:13:41.920
"I am a Sahaja Yogi. I have this power",  is not accepted.

00:13:46.480 --> 00:13:54.280
He talks about something like that, it is of no avail.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:14:01.600
As you cannot force Sahaja Yoga or anyone

00:14:01.800 --> 00:14:05.880
you cannot force yourself upon us.

00:14:12.240 --> 00:14:19.840
And we don't want dishonest hypocritical people.

00:14:20.200 --> 00:14:24.800
You have to become the genuine, the pure,

00:14:28.400 --> 00:14:33.640
otherwise how will you emit these vibrations.

00:14:37.160 --> 00:14:44.000
You are the one who has to do this new revolution.

00:14:47.080 --> 00:14:52.040
For any other revolution people had to sacrifice,

00:14:52.320 --> 00:14:57.600
had to die, there were massacres

00:15:02.200 --> 00:15:07.720
but in Sahaja Yoga you are blessed all the time, blessed.

00:15:09.280 --> 00:15:13.600
And you have to just count your blessings one by one.

00:15:16.480 --> 00:15:19.280
You are all the time blessed,

00:15:19.480 --> 00:15:25.640
all the time you are given support and help and security.

00:15:31.880 --> 00:15:37.360
Every moment you have the sensation of tremendous joy

00:15:39.880 --> 00:15:46.480
and enormous confidence in your righteousness and virtues.

00:15:51.120 --> 00:15:57.960
But as we are coming from the crowds

00:15:58.640 --> 00:16:06.480
suddenly we cannot accept, to be on a hill-top watching the crowds.

00:16:15.680 --> 00:16:19.840
Because in modern times we live in Hell.

00:16:23.440 --> 00:16:28.640
Like our one foot is in the mouth of a crocodile

00:16:32.520 --> 00:16:35.920
and here you are pulled into a boat,

00:16:37.600 --> 00:16:41.920
but if you want to be on the crocodile, or in the crocodile's mouth,

00:16:42.120 --> 00:16:45.760
nobody can help you.

00:16:49.920 --> 00:16:56.640
If you want to put back your foot into it what can anybody do?

00:16:57.920 --> 00:17:02.480
If you like that way, nobody can force you.

00:17:04.680 --> 00:17:09.360
But once you start enjoying yourself,

00:17:12.000 --> 00:17:15.680
enjoying the bliss of Divine

00:17:17.720 --> 00:17:22.520
then seldom you want to go back to the crocodile.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:32.680
The conditioning in human beings sometimes can be very strong.

00:17:36.880 --> 00:17:42.440
Specially the conditioning of the ego is horrible.

00:17:45.240 --> 00:17:49.480
Like to say, "I don't like this, I like this".

00:17:54.000 --> 00:17:58.480
or, "I hate this, I love this."

00:18:00.480 --> 00:18:05.000
When you say that 'I' where is this 'I?'

00:18:09.400 --> 00:18:13.360
You have not known yourself so far.

00:18:14.800 --> 00:18:19.360
When you become yourself, you'll never say like that,

00:18:25.480 --> 00:18:31.840
because you do not react in that manner.

00:18:32.240 --> 00:18:35.880
You just watch and see,

00:18:37.640 --> 00:18:43.280
absorb whatever is good and discard whatever is bad.

00:18:48.240 --> 00:18:53.680
But this discretion has to be established.

00:18:56.480 --> 00:19:02.280
As there are two energies within us as told by him

00:19:02.480 --> 00:19:05.800
on the left and the right,

00:19:09.880 --> 00:19:13.840
we have a tendency to go towards the left or towards the right,

00:19:14.040 --> 00:19:17.280
and go to the extremes.

00:19:22.320 --> 00:19:28.840
In France I think is people want to go to the left all the time.

00:19:32.800 --> 00:19:37.920
That is they follow people like Egyptians who think of their death

00:19:38.120 --> 00:19:42.360
and miserable and unhappy, this that.

00:19:51.680 --> 00:19:56.320
Such people take to self-destruction.

00:20:00.480 --> 00:20:04.280
They do not destroy others

00:20:04.480 --> 00:20:08.600
but in self-destruction they can  do things

00:20:08.800 --> 00:20:13.000
which they know are bad but will go on doing it.

00:20:22.120 --> 00:20:24.280
I don't want to say all of them otherwise

00:20:24.480 --> 00:20:27.760
may be half of you might go away.

00:20:32.000 --> 00:20:39.000
As you know too much drinking, smoking, you know it's bad for you.

00:20:42.680 --> 00:20:46.360
You see a person coming out of a pub and fainting

00:20:46.560 --> 00:20:48.440
and you want to go in the same pub

00:20:48.640 --> 00:20:52.040
to get the same feeling of fainting.

00:20:57.480 --> 00:21:00.720
But nobody dare say "Don't drink".

00:21:03.440 --> 00:21:05.440
It's sinful.

00:21:05.800 --> 00:21:10.560
Now, when you get your Realization I don't have to tell you.

00:21:13.920 --> 00:21:17.280
You become so powerful

00:21:18.480 --> 00:21:23.480
that you decide for yourself and you never try to destroy yourself.

00:21:27.040 --> 00:21:31.480
Overnight people have given up drugs,

00:21:33.200 --> 00:21:37.760
overnight people have given up bad habits.

00:21:40.800 --> 00:21:46.320
All kinds of nonsensical habits they have given up

00:21:49.320 --> 00:21:52.400
because now they have become the Spirit.

00:21:53.320 --> 00:21:56.440
They see themselves

00:21:56.920 --> 00:22:01.680
The left-side is very dangerous in a way.

00:22:03.480 --> 00:22:08.480
Beyond the left side resides your subconscious,

00:22:11.560 --> 00:22:17.480
then resides the subconscious of your previous lives

00:22:18.960 --> 00:22:23.720
and beyond that resides the collective subconscious.

00:22:27.960 --> 00:22:31.400
Beyond that resides all that is gone out of

00:22:31.600 --> 00:22:35.320
the evolutionary process.

00:22:40.160 --> 00:22:47.360
From there comes the triggering of all these diseases like cancer,

00:22:53.200 --> 00:22:57.560
like myelitis - all these muscular disabilities,

00:22:57.760 --> 00:23:01.240
muscular dissipation,disability,

00:23:06.480 --> 00:23:11.000
then impotency,

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:15.560
AIDS,

00:23:18.080 --> 00:23:21.680
madness, lunacy, epilepsy,

00:23:23.400 --> 00:23:26.760
all psychosomatic diseases,

00:23:28.240 --> 00:23:31.440
all psychological diseases.

00:23:32.000 --> 00:23:35.800
That is the psyche on the left-hand side.

00:23:37.200 --> 00:23:44.960
And a person like Freud, who was a half-baked man,

00:23:48.920 --> 00:23:52.800
himself was a complicated person

00:23:54.280 --> 00:23:57.840
- he had bad relation with his own mother -

00:24:01.960 --> 00:24:05.640
and who died of cancer,

00:24:05.840 --> 00:24:10.360
and he practiced on the pathological cases.

00:24:12.600 --> 00:24:17.760
Pathos means suffering.

00:24:20.240 --> 00:24:24.240
So all left-sided diseases

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:29.000
which are, which were very few in those days,

00:24:30.840 --> 00:24:34.360
and he generalized it

00:24:34.560 --> 00:24:39.720
and he propagated his Freudian theories.

00:24:42.640 --> 00:24:47.920
He was given a higher position than that of Christ.

00:24:52.800 --> 00:24:56.360
Maybe the Christianity was going on the other side

00:24:56.560 --> 00:25:00.360
of putting too much restrictions,

00:25:04.560 --> 00:25:07.440
calling human beings "sinners".

00:25:08.960 --> 00:25:12.080
Whatever may be the reason

00:25:12.280 --> 00:25:16.760
- one side the dogma another side the licentiousness -

00:25:20.640 --> 00:25:26.560
both are wrong, both are self-destructive

00:25:27.720 --> 00:25:31.600
and they are not going to give you any help.

00:25:33.400 --> 00:25:40.760
And these two things acted upon the Western people more,

00:25:45.880 --> 00:25:50.000
and they got lost into the left side.

00:25:51.200 --> 00:25:55.640
To go to the extreme they started taking drugs,

00:25:58.240 --> 00:26:02.000
and now the Aids.

00:26:03.720 --> 00:26:09.880
In Sahaja Yoga what happens that your attention comes to the center.

00:26:14.840 --> 00:26:19.000
You come on the parasympathetic nervous system.

00:26:21.480 --> 00:26:24.760
You can see like this My attention is supposing,

00:26:24.960 --> 00:26:29.520
is going this side and something pushes it upward like that.

00:26:39.520 --> 00:26:41.840
So, when the Kundalini rises

00:26:42.040 --> 00:26:44.840
She brings your attention collected from everywhere,

00:26:45.040 --> 00:26:49.880
brings it upward and pierces through your fontanel bone area.

00:26:58.880 --> 00:27:02.640
But also we have very many right-sided people.

00:27:05.440 --> 00:27:10.240
They went in other countries and tried to dominate them.

00:27:14.200 --> 00:27:16.760
I sometimes say thank God Columbus

00:27:16.960 --> 00:27:21.480
did not come to India, otherwise I would not have been here.

00:27:26.480 --> 00:27:30.480
He went to America and finished off all of them.

00:27:33.040 --> 00:27:37.400
So this is the right-sidedness when we destroy others.

00:27:38.400 --> 00:27:42.920
In that we have a kind of a ego ,

00:27:43.120 --> 00:27:46.360
we think we are better than others.

00:27:49.520 --> 00:27:51.560
This is falsehood.

00:27:52.280 --> 00:27:56.480
God has not created anybody higher or lower.

00:27:58.560 --> 00:28:04.800
God created only one world and human beings.

00:28:05.000 --> 00:28:09.520
Only according to the climate we are varied -

00:28:09.720 --> 00:28:12.680
we are different from each other.

00:28:16.280 --> 00:28:18.640
And variety is so important

00:28:18.840 --> 00:28:24.480
otherwise we'd all would be just the same,

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:30.840
like military regime of human beings,

00:28:35.600 --> 00:28:38.480
or maybe like robots.

00:28:39.480 --> 00:28:42.680
But He made us so separate and different

00:28:42.880 --> 00:28:47.440
because we bring beauty in this world.

00:28:52.720 --> 00:28:56.800
That life is interesting.

00:28:58.120 --> 00:29:05.400
One leaf of a tree is not just the same as another leaf.

00:29:09.720 --> 00:29:14.000
Just see the tremendous work of art.

00:29:16.480 --> 00:29:18.440
In the same artistic way

00:29:18.640 --> 00:29:23.360
He has created human beings in different manners.

00:29:27.320 --> 00:29:31.840
But we think we are different,

00:29:32.040 --> 00:29:36.000
they are different - this is our own conditioning.

00:29:45.040 --> 00:29:50.480
These are all flowers on one tree.

00:29:53.680 --> 00:29:57.720
But we haven't got the sense of collective

00:29:59.120 --> 00:30:02.400
that's why we think like that.

00:30:03.080 --> 00:30:06.920
We cannot feel the connection with others.

00:30:08.520 --> 00:30:12.560
It's like you may form a club.

00:30:13.480 --> 00:30:17.720
Like you have club of people who use fork and spoon

00:30:17.920 --> 00:30:21.240
in a different manner.

00:30:27.840 --> 00:30:31.760
There are all sorts of funny clubs.

00:30:33.920 --> 00:30:37.720
We try to club together,

00:30:39.120 --> 00:30:41.480
artificially.

00:30:41.840 --> 00:30:48.440
Whatever is artificially we are doing exists in reality also.

00:30:51.720 --> 00:30:55.720
We are part and parcel of one whole.

00:30:58.040 --> 00:31:03.000
The microcosm belongs to the macrocosm, no doubt,

00:31:05.680 --> 00:31:09.480
but it's not the reality with us yet.

00:31:11.080 --> 00:31:13.760
It's just an idea.

00:31:13.960 --> 00:31:16.560
So under anything you can have a league

00:31:16.760 --> 00:31:20.480
- like somebody has a "red hair league" -

00:31:25.160 --> 00:31:28.800
and then we try to classify them.

00:31:31.600 --> 00:31:38.000
It's all so artificial and so stupid.

00:31:39.760 --> 00:31:42.480
You are part and parcel of the whole

00:31:42.680 --> 00:31:47.480
and you cannot classify yourself as separate.

00:31:52.840 --> 00:31:57.600
Like this hand and this hand belongs to this body.

00:32:01.480 --> 00:32:04.960
Now if this hand wants to soothe the other hand

00:32:05.160 --> 00:32:08.720
is it doing any obligation on this hand?

00:32:17.320 --> 00:32:22.960
So after Realization you feel who is the other?

00:32:27.200 --> 00:32:33.480
We don't aggress with our hands our nose, do we?

00:32:37.360 --> 00:32:41.880
We don't put our finger into our eyes to aggress it, do we?

00:32:45.280 --> 00:32:48.560
Because the eye is whiter than the finger

00:32:48.760 --> 00:32:52.480
- do we put our finger into it?

00:32:55.920 --> 00:33:00.400
All this aggressiveness is that stupid.

00:33:03.880 --> 00:33:10.520
If you are aggressing each other you are aggressing the whole.

00:33:12.640 --> 00:33:19.480
Anywhere you try to do that, you harm the other part of the whole.

00:33:23.920 --> 00:33:27.600
Then we start having organization for the whole-

00:33:27.800 --> 00:33:32.640
The Whole World International Organization - this and that.

00:33:38.280 --> 00:33:44.000
But the people inside that, are they collectively conscious?

00:33:51.600 --> 00:33:56.560
Is that their inner understanding

00:33:56.760 --> 00:34:03.400
on their central nervous system that other doesn't exist?

00:34:10.120 --> 00:34:15.000
So this problem also gets solved after Sahaja Yoga.

00:34:17.880 --> 00:34:23.960
You forget that you are only a Frenchman and nothing more.

00:34:26.720 --> 00:34:30.800
Like a drop falls into the ocean and becomes the ocean

00:34:31.000 --> 00:34:36.400
the heart of a Sahaja Yogi becomes so great.

00:34:42.360 --> 00:34:45.280
He doesn't see the color of your skin,

00:34:45.480 --> 00:34:49.480
