And those who haven't got it, might get it today.

01:52:37.800 --> 01:52:43.360
Those who have come for the first time also will get Realization.

01:52:46.600 --> 01:52:51.520
Whether you get it here or not,

01:52:52.880 --> 01:52:59.800
you must go to our centers to establish it.

