Now, please put both your feet on the Mother Earth, like this,

01:53:42.160 --> 01:53:46.000
and keep them separate.

01:53:46.920 --> 01:53:50.680
Please keep them separate.

01:53:52.160 --> 01:53:55.920
Now,

01:53:59.840 --> 01:54:04.800
you have to put your left hand towards Me.

01:54:08.560 --> 01:54:13.320
