So we are going to use the right hand,

01:54:34.640 --> 01:54:40.120
for facilitating the Kundalini to rise.

01:54:43.840 --> 01:54:46.440
And for that

01:54:46.640 --> 01:54:51.880
you have to just follow what I tell you.

01:54:55.080 --> 01:55:02.280
We are working on the left-hand side of your centers.

01:55:06.080 --> 01:55:08.240
So, first of all we put our hand -

01:55:08.440 --> 01:55:11.240
- this I'm telling you what we have to do, but you follow Me -

01:55:11.440 --> 01:55:15.280
right hand on the heart.

01:55:21.200 --> 01:55:27.520
Now, in the heart is the reflection of God Almighty.

01:55:29.920 --> 01:55:32.120
Then we take down our hand

01:55:32.320 --> 01:55:37.320
in the upper part of our abdomen, on the left-hand side.

01:55:41.600 --> 01:55:46.720
Here resides the center of our mastery.

01:55:48.960 --> 01:55:53.040
All the great masters, prophets who came on this earth

01:55:53.240 --> 01:55:58.360
have established and substantiated this center.

01:56:06.200 --> 01:56:09.920
Then we put our hand in the lower portion of our abdomen,

01:56:10.120 --> 01:56:13.960
in the left-hand side.

01:56:18.200 --> 01:56:26.000
Now, this is the center which is for our true knowledge,

01:56:26.200 --> 01:56:32.080
to be manifested within us of the Divine power.

01:56:40.320 --> 01:56:42.440
Now again we go back

01:56:42.640 --> 01:56:46.840
onto the upper portion of our abdomen, on the left-hand side.

01:56:51.600 --> 01:56:56.440
Then we take our right hand again on the heart.

01:57:00.120 --> 01:57:05.360
Then we take this right hand in the corner of your neck, here,

01:57:05.560 --> 01:57:10.280
and put your head to your right side.

01:57:24.960 --> 01:57:28.040
Turn your head to your right.

01:57:29.440 --> 01:57:35.240
This center catches when we are feeling guilty.

01:57:38.800 --> 01:57:42.560
Today also most of you are catching this center.

01:57:45.960 --> 01:57:48.240
Now, take out this hand

01:57:48.440 --> 01:57:54.040
and put it on your forehead across and press it on both the sides.

01:57:59.360 --> 01:58:03.600
So, this is the center of forgiveness,

01:58:05.480 --> 01:58:08.480
the power of forgiveness.

01:58:08.960 --> 01:58:13.520
Take this hand on the back of your head

01:58:15.480 --> 01:58:18.520
and put your hand in such a manner

01:58:18.720 --> 01:58:23.680
that you can hold your head which is reclining on it.

01:58:29.160 --> 01:58:33.040
Now, stretch your hand,

01:58:37.200 --> 01:58:45.200
and place the center of your palm on top of the fontanel bone area

01:58:51.080 --> 01:58:57.520
and push back your fingers.

01:58:58.280 --> 01:59:01.720
Press the scalp

01:59:01.920 --> 01:59:08.560
and slowly you move it in a clockwise manner, seven times.

01:59:20.040 --> 01:59:23.760
Now, that's all we have to do.

01:59:23.960 --> 01:59:27.360
But you have to keep your eyes shut.

01:59:28.480 --> 01:59:31.640
Both the feet on the ground

01:59:31.840 --> 01:59:35.360
and the left hand towards Me like this, little higher,

01:59:36.040 --> 01:59:39.840
little higher like that.

01:59:41.960 --> 01:59:46.840
Now, we start off by closing our eyes.

01:59:47.920 --> 01:59:52.280
But we are not to open our eyes till I tell you,

01:59:55.480 --> 01:59:59.080
because the attention has to go inside.

02:00:00.120 --> 02:00:03.440
Now don't fight with your thoughts,

02:00:05.280 --> 02:00:07.800
just leave it alone.

02:00:08.640 --> 02:00:12.160
Kundalini will take charge of everything.

02:00:14.920 --> 02:00:20.520
All right. Now put your right hand on your heart.

02:00:24.360 --> 02:00:28.800
And you must put all your worries aside.

02:00:31.640 --> 02:00:33.720
Also you should forgive yourself

02:00:33.920 --> 02:00:38.440
and should be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

02:00:43.400 --> 02:00:46.520
Now, when your hand is on your heart,

02:00:46.760 --> 02:00:49.680
you have to ask Me a fundamental question.

02:00:49.880 --> 02:00:53.040
If you want, you can call Me Shri Mataji or Mother,

02:00:53.240 --> 02:00:56.120
whatever suits you, and the question is

02:00:56.320 --> 02:01:02.120
"Mother, am I the Spirit?" Ask this question three times.

02:01:18.880 --> 02:01:22.480
Ask this question three times.

02:01:39.560 --> 02:01:42.920
Now with this another question comes in

02:01:43.120 --> 02:01:47.400
that if you are the Spirit you become your master.

02:01:47.680 --> 02:01:51.440
So put your right hand on the right side,

02:01:51.680 --> 02:01:56.120
on the left side of your abdomen, in the upper part.

02:02:09.160 --> 02:02:12.600
Now, so ask another question here three times,

02:02:12.800 --> 02:02:17.040
"Mother, am I my own master?"

02:02:21.800 --> 02:02:24.760
Keep your neck straight.

02:02:26.760 --> 02:02:29.320
Please keep your neck straight and sit straight

02:02:29.520 --> 02:02:33.120
and do not droop forward or backwards.

02:03:03.400 --> 02:03:10.160
Now put this right hand on the lower part of your abdomen

02:03:12.160 --> 02:03:14.760
- on the left hand side.

02:03:14.960 --> 02:03:20.640
Here I cannot cross over your freedom,

02:03:23.040 --> 02:03:26.160
so you have to ask.

02:03:27.960 --> 02:03:34.720
Please ask, "Mother, may I have the pure knowledge?"

02:03:38.040 --> 02:03:41.920
"Mother, please give me pure knowledge."

02:03:43.520 --> 02:03:49.320
Please say this six times because this center has got six petals.

02:04:02.440 --> 02:04:04.720
Now,

02:04:07.520 --> 02:04:12.200
the Kundalini starts moving with this asking.

02:04:16.200 --> 02:04:21.960
To facilitate Her movement in the upper centers,

02:04:26.480 --> 02:04:28.960
we have to put our right hand

02:04:29.160 --> 02:04:35.160
in the upper portion of your abdomen on the left-hand side.

02:04:40.080 --> 02:04:43.480
Here you have to say

02:04:44.160 --> 02:04:47.440
with full confidence,

02:04:47.640 --> 02:04:52.040
to facilitate the Kundalini to move

02:04:53.760 --> 02:04:56.960
in this center of mastery.

02:04:59.440 --> 02:05:05.960
Please say it ten times "Mother, I am my master".

02:05:11.320 --> 02:05:15.600
Say it with full confidence.

02:05:34.920 --> 02:05:44.200
Now we have to know that we are the Spirit.

02:05:45.400 --> 02:05:48.880
We are not this body,

02:05:49.080 --> 02:05:54.960
not this ego, not this conditioning,

02:05:55.640 --> 02:06:00.320
but in reality we are the Spirit.

02:06:00.920 --> 02:06:05.520
Now put your right hand on your heart again

02:06:07.760 --> 02:06:11.440
and say with full confidence twelve times,

02:06:11.640 --> 02:06:17.560
"Mother, I am the Spirit."

02:06:43.080 --> 02:06:51.080
Now, we have to know also that the Divine is the ocean of

02:06:51.640 --> 02:06:59.640
bliss, grace and compassion.

02:07:05.600 --> 02:07:10.440
But above all, it is the ocean of forgiveness.

02:07:13.080 --> 02:07:24.360
And we cannot do any mistake that it cannot engulf it.

02:07:28.240 --> 02:07:32.960
So, please forgive yourself first of all.

02:07:34.120 --> 02:07:41.400
Put your right hand on the left - hand shoulder

02:07:45.840 --> 02:07:49.800
and turn your head to your right,

02:07:50.000 --> 02:07:51.880
fully.

02:07:52.560 --> 02:07:55.520
Now here you have to say with full confidence,

02:07:55.720 --> 02:08:01.560
"Mother, I am not guilty at all."

02:08:06.160 --> 02:08:10.520
Say it sixteen times

02:08:14.800 --> 02:08:17.400
and if you still feel guilty

02:08:17.600 --> 02:08:23.640
better punish yourself by saying 108 times.

02:08:29.840 --> 02:08:34.840
You have to be pleasantly placed towards yourself.

02:08:35.520 --> 02:08:40.080
You are entering into the kingdom of God.

02:09:02.000 --> 02:09:07.920
Now, put your hand on your forehead across

02:09:10.080 --> 02:09:13.840
and press it hard.

02:09:14.040 --> 02:09:17.120
Here you have to say,

02:09:17.320 --> 02:09:21.120
"Mother, I forgive everyone."

02:09:23.720 --> 02:09:26.920
On your forehead please.

02:09:27.680 --> 02:09:31.640
They are not putting it. On your forehead, not on your head,

02:09:31.840 --> 02:09:34.920
and press it hard.

02:09:35.280 --> 02:09:39.640
Now some may say it's difficult to say,

02:09:40.600 --> 02:09:45.760
but whether you forgive or you don't forgive it's a myth.

02:09:47.520 --> 02:09:50.080
But if you don't forgive you play into wrong hands,

02:09:50.280 --> 02:09:55.800
so say, "Mother, I forgive everyone", from your heart.

02:10:06.000 --> 02:10:10.440
Now take your hand on the back of your head

02:10:10.640 --> 02:10:16.840
and raise, turn your head on it, to rest on it.

02:10:24.280 --> 02:10:28.480
Here for your own satisfaction you can say,

02:10:28.680 --> 02:10:32.560
"Oh Divine, if I have done anything wrong, please forgive me",

02:10:32.760 --> 02:10:34.400
but for your own satisfaction,

02:10:34.600 --> 02:10:38.040
not to feel guilty, not to count your mistakes.

02:10:54.280 --> 02:10:58.840
You have to love yourself, you have to respect yourself.

02:11:01.000 --> 02:11:06.040
You have been created into human-being with great difficulties.

02:11:08.800 --> 02:11:13.600
Now, stretch your hand, right hand.

02:11:16.440 --> 02:11:22.640
Put the middle of center of your palm, on top of the fontanel bone,

02:11:26.000 --> 02:11:31.440
and now press it hard and move it seven times slowly.

02:11:39.320 --> 02:11:46.920
Here also I cannot force you to Self-Realization.

02:11:50.960 --> 02:11:54.280
So you have to ask,

02:11:54.880 --> 02:11:59.960
"Mother, please give me my Self-Realization."

02:12:01.560 --> 02:12:04.520
Seven times.

02:12:04.720 --> 02:12:08.680
